Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: Any animal companion a blightlord possesses gains the blightspawned template. This provides immunity to poison, immunity to sleep, immunity to paralysis, immunity to stunning, immunity to critical hits and sneak attacks, and immunity to mind-affecting effects. The companion also recieves the following ability changes: Str +4, Con +2, Wis -2, and Cha -2. Their natural attacks also inflict the same blight that the blightlord's blight touch ability confers.
Use: Automatic.